data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 109 Colliers Way. This spacious house boasts 4 large bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, perfect for accommodating a growing family or hosting guests. The front and backyards are also generously sized, providing ample space for outdoor activities and entertainment. Plus, there is an outdoor shed for extra storage and organization. The convenient location of this property puts you just minutes away from major highways, allowing for easy commuting and access to nearby amenities. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your next home. Schedule a showing today!
